## Tutorial
tutorial.main.continue=Continue
tutorial.main.1=Welcome to the spider-verse!
tutorial.main.2=Each of your different hotbar slots represents a move.
tutorial.main.3=To activate (do) the move, jump whilst in the air with your selected slot.
tutorial.main.4=There will be a name tab on the side of your hotbar that tells you what that slot does.
tutorial.main.5=For each slot, you can also crouch to use its charged activation.
tutorial.main.6=By holding sneak in your 9th slot, you can activate your suit!
tutorial.main.7=When your suit is active, you can switch to other slots to see what they do.
tutorial.main.8=For instance, the 8th slot is a suit customisation menu!
tutorial.main.9=By jumping next to a wall you can wall jump.
tutorial.main.10=You get 3 of these for every wall, but can reset this by jumping back and forth.
tutorial.main.11=The combat in this add-on is very dynamic.
tutorial.main.12=There are over 25 unique special combos, with loads of additional possible combos.
tutorial.main.13=You can learn more about these on MCPEDL/discord, or simply by experimenting.
tutorial.main.14=When you're swinging around, aim opposite the direction of the wall you're swinging alongside.
tutorial.main.15=This will steer you away from hitting the wall, and makes swinging a lot easier.
tutorial.main.16=There's definitely a learning curve, but once you get it, it's so much fun!
tutorial.main.17=Best of luck out there!

